'''[[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] commandeered an [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeder]]''' from the forces of [[Iaco Stark/Legends|Iaco Stark]]. Using it, she, [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]], and [[Qui-Gon Jinn/Legends|Qui-Gon Jinn]] evacuated [[Senator/Legends|Senators]] [[Nute Gunray/Legends|Nute Gunray]] and [[Finis Valorum/Legends|Finis Valorum]] from [[Mount Avos]]. They took the Senators to Stark's headquarters, where they stole his personal ship to return to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].<ref name="SW38">[[Star Wars (1998) 38|''Star Wars'' (1998) 38]]</ref>

